{"type":"message","id":"d5e807ba","parentId":"5f9dabf6","timestamp":"2026-03-28T01:25:43.518Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Done! I've completed the self-learning task. Let me summarize what was done.","thinkingSignature":"8e7287ce599e5cdb05770c152ebc275f9801c2e8ef6d259c5a01966a686353bf"},{"type":"text","text":"**自主学习完成** ✅\n\n**无活跃对话**，已执行自主学习任务：\n\n1. **搜索整合了4个领域的最新行业动态**：\n   - 企业数字化转型（2026政策+趋势）\n   - 智能安防与弱电工程（8000亿市场）\n   - IT运维服务（AIOps千亿市场）\n   - 网络系统集成（4000亿市场）\n\n2. **整理了5大核心洞察**，涵盖政策补贴（15%补贴/5000万封顶）、市场规模预测、技术趋势（AIoT/数字孪生/零信任/全光网络）、模式转型（工程→服务化/卖人天→卖效果）\n\n3. **已保存**至 `/home/gem/workspace/agent/workspace/memory/学习笔记.md`"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6778,"output":186,"cacheRead":43981,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":50945,"cost":{"input":0.0020334,"output":0.00022319999999999998,"cacheRead":0.00131943,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0035760299999999996}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774661139015}}
